      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Federico Andrés Corigliano</b>\n</p><p><b>Federico Andrés Corigliano</b>,<br />\nan Argentinian computer scientist and as computer chess programmer author of the chess engine <a href=\"/Chispa\" title=\"Chispa\">Chispa</a>, which was one of the first <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a> engines, and the open source engine <a href=\"/HeavyChess\" title=\"HeavyChess\">HeavyChess</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2001\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2001</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2002\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2002</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2003\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2003</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2004\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2004</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Federico_Andr%C3%A9s_Corigliano&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2001\">2001</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Federico_Andr%C3%A9s_Corigliano&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2001\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=183787\">ELO of the chess programs in the 2010</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 15, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">Playing Strength</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=186640\">The Crazy Bishop 0046 and Gromit 3.8.2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 31, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/The_Crazy_Bishop\" title=\"The Crazy Bishop\">The Crazy Bishop</a>, <a href=\"/Gromit\" title=\"Gromit\">Gromit</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=187335\">What is the amateur program with the best opening book for you?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 05, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=193986\">Make a engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 23, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=195009\">Fritz 7 size in bytes</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 30, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Fritz\" title=\"Fritz\">Fritz</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2002\">2002</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Federico_Andr%C3%A9s_Corigliano&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2002\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=232560\">OT Question to all programmers</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 28, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=239736\">OT About Malvinas-Falklands Islands. A poll</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 10, 2002 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=269951\">Question about Hash-tables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 10, 2002</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2003\">2003</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Federico_Andr%C3%A9s_Corigliano&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2003\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=276072\">How to run the Javachess from GameDev.net?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 09, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=40827&amp;p=155641\">I send to Ed the new Chispa 1.54</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 18, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=277752\">Slighty OT: Profiling</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 16, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=41627&amp;p=158817\">Chispa 2.1 is available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 09, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=42286&amp;p=161513\">Chispa 3.0 beta 5 is available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, April 18, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=310897\">Regarding Qsearch with Fractional ply extensions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 11, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a>, <a href=\"/Depth#FractionalPlies\" title=\"Depth\">Depth - Fractional Plies</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=311344\">To Ed: Branching factor formula in Rebel 12</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 15, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Branching_Factor\" title=\"Branching Factor\">Branching Factor</a>, <a href=\"/Rebel\" title=\"Rebel\">Rebel</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=311601\">Speed improvement in split move generation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 16, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=43819&amp;p=167366\">Chispa news</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, August 18, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=333144\">int vs short int</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 02, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=334370\">To programmers: Hints for testing after a partial rewrite</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 08, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=335845\">I use this in Chispa</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 13, 2003  </li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2004\">2004</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Federico_Andr%C3%A9s_Corigliano&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2004\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=339934\">I need your opinion about this hash entry structure</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 02, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=342372\">Resources about rotated bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 02, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Rotated_Bitboards\" title=\"Rotated Bitboards\">Rotated Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=45891&amp;p=174306\">Today is Chispa's First Birthday</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 04, 2004 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=342885\">C++ Programming Q: are const and define efficiency the same</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 16, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=49061&amp;p=185165\">Chispa 4.0 Pre-Release 1 is ready</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Federico Corigliano</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 25, 2004</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_